                               A COMPARISON
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~

 Because there is often a discussion about the best painting program on
 ST, I will comparise the mostly used of these programs, which are :

 a.) -DPAINT ST
 b.) -NEOCHROME 2.28
 c.) -CRACKART 1.36 TT

  ________________________________________________________________
 | name     |    DPAINT ST   |   NEO 2.28     |  CRACKART 1.36    |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------|
